metadata.name: Odyssey
metadata.description:
The magical waters are colored in gorgeous colors under the softly setting dusk.  
The shore is far behind, and only the phantom singing of birds can be heard.  
The abandoned city of the past is far behind, the ferry swaying gently on the almost ephemeral waters.  
The smell of the breeze, everything is so clean.  
Uncommon places, heart and soul.

Odyssey.

**"Odyssey" is an exclusive BWOW inspired airdrop, created by Blank Embrace, for holders of "By Way of Water"**

attributes.value: Blank Embrace X By Way of Water
